ALSA: usb-audio: Set correct type for some UAC2 mixer controls.

Changed ctl type for Input Gain Control and Input Gain Pad Control to
USB_MIXER_S16 as per section 5.2.5.7.11-12 in the USB Audio Class 2.0
definition.

